## 5. Product Vision

SchemeSeva becomes the civic AI layer between Indian citizens and India's welfare system — knowing who you are, finding what you're entitled to, and watching so you never miss a new benefit. Hackathon build: 25–30 verified central + Telangana schemes, demonstrating all five agentic verbs in one TypeScript system.

**Primary differentiator:** Click the Simulate button during the demo. The Vigilance Agent finds the citizen without being asked. myScheme will never do that. No existing government portal does.

