### 6.6 User Stories with Acceptance Criteria

**US-001 — Natural Language Profile Intake**
As a citizen, I want to describe myself in plain language so I don't fill a rigid form.
- AC: Accepts free-text; extracts state, age, gender, category, income, occupation minimum
- AC: Asks exactly one follow-up if critical field missing; never assumes income or category
- AC: Profile extraction under 10 seconds

**US-002 — Semantic Scheme Discovery**
As a citizen, I want the agent to find all schemes I may qualify for.
- AC: 3+ relevant schemes for any complete farmer, student, or entrepreneur profile
- AC: Both central and Telangana state schemes returned where applicable
- AC: Minimum 3 different semantic query angles; duplicates removed

**US-003 — Eligibility Validation with Confidence**
As a citizen, I want each scheme to show whether I truly qualify.
- AC: Every scheme has confidence: "high" or "medium"
- AC: Hard-failed criteria (wrong gender, income over limit) excluded entirely — not shown with low confidence
- AC: Missing-document list shown for medium-confidence schemes
- AC: Eligibility is deterministic rule-based, not LLM-guessed

**US-004 — Actionable Plain-Language Report**
As a citizen, I want a report with exact steps so I can act immediately.
- AC: Each scheme: name, benefit, why-qualify (2 sentences), numbered steps, doc checklist, applicationUrl, sourceUrl, lastVerified
- AC: 8th-grade reading level; no jargon
- AC: Sorted by benefit value descending
- AC: "likely eligible" used throughout; one disclaimer at end

**US-005 — Enkrypt AI Safety Validation**
As a citizen, I want every piece of guidance to have been checked for accuracy.
- AC: 100% of Report Agent outputs through Enkrypt before returned
- AC: Flagged output regenerated once; second failure shows "Unverified" warning
- AC: Enkrypt validation logged server-side on every /api/discover call
- AC: "✓ Validated by Enkrypt AI" badge visible on SchemeReport

**US-006 — Proactive Vigilance Alert**
As a returning citizen, I want to be notified when a new scheme matches me without asking.
- AC: Simulate button injects new scheme into Qdrant; Vigilance Agent returns alert within 5 seconds
- AC: AlertBanner shows scheme name, reason, urgency
- AC: Alert validated by Enkrypt before display

**US-007 — Session Memory**
As a returning citizen, I want the agent to remember me.
- AC: Session ID in localStorage; CitizenProfile in Qdrant citizen_sessions
- AC: "Start Fresh" option clears session

