## 10. UI/UX Documentation

### Design Goals
- Function first — working demo beats polished mockup
- Legibility over decoration — 8th-grade reading level everywhere
- Pipeline visibility — loading step labels are the Mastra judging story
- Trust signals on screen — Enkrypt badge, confidence badges, sourceUrl, lastVerified without scrolling
- One-screen demo flow — profile → loading → report → simulate → alert all in one uninterrupted session

